        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You can control and manage cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow users to block or delete cookies. However, restricting cookies may impact website functionality.</p>
        
